            <title>[GROOVY-2404] A lost funktion in GSQL</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-2404</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Following statement run in groovy 1.1B3:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;dbh.eachRow(&apos;select * from employees&apos;) &lt;/p&gt;
{row-&amp;gt;
  String fieldname = &apos;LAST_NAME&apos;
  println row[fieldname]
   }

&lt;p&gt;in the new version 1.5 is this not more possible.&lt;br/&gt;
This functionality was very usefull and fancy!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The workaraond &lt;br/&gt;
Integer colInx = row.findColumn(name)&lt;br/&gt;
println       row&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;colInx-1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ist painfull to make in a huge programm.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;#94;/ili&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
